<$transclude $tiddler="$:/plugins/rimir/doc-template/templates/page">
<$fill $name="body">

!! Plugin files

|!File |!Role |
|`EXPLIDE.tid` |Main IDE template — config fields, layout toggle, `$testcase` assembly |
|`variables.tid` |Shared filter functions (`rri.*`) |
|`core-integration/ViewTemplate.tid` |Hooks into TW ViewTemplate for `rri.type: explide/config` |
|`ide-templates/tab.tid` |Top-level tab content (CONFIG, ADHOC, DIAGNOSTICS, explide data, imported tiddlers) |
|`ide-templates/tabButton.tid` |Top-level tab button labels |
|`ide-templates/explide/tabTemplate.tid` |Explide data sub-tabs (EDITOR, FIELDS, DIFF) with snapshot UI |
|`ide-templates/config/plugins/tab.tid` |Plugin config — import toggle, shadow tiddler list, delete button, bulk import |
|`ide-templates/adhoc-tiddlers/tab.tid` |Ad-hoc tiddler editor |
|`ide-templates/diagnostics/tab.tid` |Diagnostics checks (missing, unused, stale) |
|`examples/*.json` |Bundled example config tiddlers |
|`styles/base.css` |Plugin-specific styles (extends `rr-*` from theme) |
|`doc/overview.tid` |Doc-template overview page |
|`doc/architecture.tid` |Architecture documentation |
|`doc/dev-workflow.tid` |Dev workflow and plugin files reference |
|`doc/examples.tid` |Usage examples documentation |
|`doc/faq.tid` |Frequently asked questions |
|`doc/reference.tid` |Config fields, filter functions, IDE tabs reference |
|`doc/tw-internals.tid` |TiddlyWiki internals used by explide |

!! Restart rules

|!Change |!Restart needed? |
|Any `.tid` or `.json` file |Yes — plugin shadow tiddlers require restart |
|`base.css` |Yes — plugin shadow tiddler |

<$transclude $tiddler="$:/plugins/rimir/doc-template/templates/callout" type="tip">
<$fill $name="body">
Explide is 100% wikitext — no JS modules at all. However, since all files are plugin shadow tiddlers, a server restart is needed to pick up changes.
</$fill>
</$transclude>

!! Dependencies

* ''theme'' — CSS utility classes (`rr-input-row`, `rr-input`, `rr-muted`, `rr-small`, `rr-callout-*`)
* ''components'' — `tabs` facade component
* ''shiraz'' — `slider` macro

!! Dev samples

The `_DEV/` directory contains sample config tiddlers and test data for development. These are not included in the published plugin.

</$fill>
</$transclude>
